hh3cFcPing.name: hh3cFcPing

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

hh3cFcPing.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cFcPing.description: This MIB module is for the management of the Fibre Channel Ping functionality.

hh3cFcPingTable.name: hh3cFcPingTable
hh3cFcPingTable.description: A table of FC ping entries containing a group of FC ping requests that need to be executed at the agent.

hh3cFcPingEntry.name: hh3cFcPingEntry
hh3cFcPingEntry.description: A FC ping request entry that need to be executed at the agent.

hh3cFcPingIndex.name: hh3cFcPingIndex
hh3cFcPingIndex.description: The index of the current FC ping entry. This object identifies a FC ping request entry uniquely in a specified VSAN (Virtual Storage Area Network).

hh3cFcPingVsan.name: hh3cFcPingVsan
hh3cFcPingVsan.description: The VSAN on which the FC ping request will be performed. If the corresponding instance value of hh3cFcPingOperStatus is 'inProgress', the object cannot be modified.

hh3cFcPingAddressType.name: hh3cFcPingAddressType
hh3cFcPingAddressType.description: The type of the corresponding instance of hh3cFcPingAddress object.

hh3cFcPingAddress.name: hh3cFcPingAddress
hh3cFcPingAddress.description: The address to which the route will be pinged. This object will contain an 8 octet long WWN(World Wide Name), if the value of the associated instance of hh3cFcPingAddressType object is 'wwn'. This object will contain a 3 octet long Fibre Channel Address ID, if the value of the associated instance of hh3cFcPingAddressType object is 'fcid'.

hh3cFcPingPacketCount.name: hh3cFcPingPacketCount
hh3cFcPingPacketCount.description: The number of FC ping packets to be sent to the target in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingPayloadSize.name: hh3cFcPingPayloadSize
hh3cFcPingPayloadSize.description: This object specifies the size of the FC ping packet payload to be sent to the target in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingTimeout.name: hh3cFcPingTimeout
hh3cFcPingTimeout.description: The value of timeout for this FC ping request.

hh3cFcPingDelay.name: hh3cFcPingDelay
hh3cFcPingDelay.description: The minimum amount of time to wait before sending the next packet in a sequence, after receiving a response or declaring a timeout for a previously transmitted packet.

hh3cFcPingAgeInterval.name: hh3cFcPingAgeInterval
hh3cFcPingAgeInterval.description: The interval time after a FC ping test completes before the entry is aged out.

hh3cFcPingAdminStatus.name: hh3cFcPingAdminStatus
hh3cFcPingAdminStatus.description: The administrative status of each hh3cFcPingEntry. The object has two values: enable - Activate the entry. disable - Deactivate the entry. When the FC ping entry is executing, this object cannot be modified. If this object is read at such a time, a value of 'enable' will be returned. When the test finishes, the value of this object will be set to 'disable'.

hh3cFcPingOperStatus.name: hh3cFcPingOperStatus
hh3cFcPingOperStatus.description: This object indicates the operational status of this hh3cFcPingEntry. The value specifications are listed as follows: inProgress - FC ping is in progress. complete - FC ping is complete. disabled - FC ping is disabled. failed - FC ping has failed due to resource limitations.

hh3cFcPingTrapOnCompletion.name: hh3cFcPingTrapOnCompletion
hh3cFcPingTrapOnCompletion.description: This object indicates that if hh3cFcPingCompletionNotify notification should be generated or not when the corresponding ping sequence completes.

hh3cFcPingRowStatus.name: hh3cFcPingRowStatus
hh3cFcPingRowStatus.description: The status of this conceptual row.

hh3cFcPingStatTable.name: hh3cFcPingStatTable
hh3cFcPingStatTable.description: A table of FC ping statistics. This table notes the FC ping statistics of a FC ping test associated with an entry in the hh3cFcPingTable.

hh3cFcPingStatEntry.name: hh3cFcPingStatEntry
hh3cFcPingStatEntry.description: A FC ping statistics entry. An entry will be created automatically in this table when the hh3cFcPingRowStatus of a ping request in the hh3cFcPingTable is set to 'active'. The entry in this table will have the same indices as the entry that in the hh3cFcPingTable. An entry in this table will be deleted when the corresponding entry in the hh3cFcPingTable is deleted.

hh3cFcPingReqPackets.name: hh3cFcPingReqPackets
hh3cFcPingReqPackets.description: The number of FC ping packets request in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingResPackets.name: hh3cFcPingResPackets
hh3cFcPingResPackets.description: The number of FC ping packets response in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingMinTime.name: hh3cFcPingMinTime
hh3cFcPingMinTime.description: The minimum round trip time of all the packets that have been sent in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingAverageTime.name: hh3cFcPingAverageTime
hh3cFcPingAverageTime.description: The average round trip time of all the packets that have been sent in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingMaxTime.name: hh3cFcPingMaxTime
hh3cFcPingMaxTime.description: The maximum round trip time of all the packets that have been sent in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingTimeoutNum.name: hh3cFcPingTimeoutNum
hh3cFcPingTimeoutNum.description: The number of timeouts encountered in this sequence.

hh3cFcPingCompletionNotify.name: hh3cFcPingCompletionNotify
hh3cFcPingCompletionNotify.description: When a FC ping test is finished and the instance of hh3cFcPingTrapOnCompletion associated with the test is set to 'true', this notification occurred.
